Marcia Van Dyke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcia_Van_Dyke 0 Marcia Van Dyke (March 26, 1922 – November 11, 2002) was an American violinist and actress. She was featured in a cover story in the January 19, 1948, issue of Life magazine. Marcia_Van_Dyke ( March_26_,_1922 – November_11_,_2002 ) was an_American_violinist_and_actress .
